    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A case made for storing and transporting a violin, which is a stringed instrument. The case is often made of molded leather or plastic and lined in velvet or another soft fabric.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
